flowchart LR
    Staff[Staff dashboard]
    Patient[Patient guidance]
    Doctor[Doctor brief]
    Frontend[React frontend\nshared polling context]
    API[Hono API\nCloudflare Worker]
    Scheduler[Pure deterministic\nscheduling engine]
    Simulation[One-minute simulation\nclock and event planner]
    DB[(Turso / libSQL\noperational state, events, metrics)]
    LLM[Gemini via\nprovider adapter]
    Cache[(Cached LLM output)]

    Staff --> Frontend
    Patient --> Frontend
    Doctor --> Frontend
    Frontend -->|GET operations, brief| API
    Frontend -->|POST one-minute tick| API
    API --> Simulation
    Simulation --> Scheduler
    Simulation <--> DB
    API <--> DB
    API -->|facts only| LLM
    LLM --> Cache
    Cache --> API

